Package com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport

Contains classes for the service that reports on changes to items in the Analysis Repository.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbsoluteBoundary
    A Boundary that specifies one end of a range of Item versions to be the very first or very last of all versions.
    Boundary
    A specifier for one end of a range of Item versions, for use when requesting an ItemHistory.
    CardComparison
    A representation of the differences between two versions of the same Card.
    CardMergeInfo
    The identifier of an original Card in its host Item, together with the identifier of the copied Card that was created during a merge operation.
    CoreItemComparison
    The core parts of an ItemComparison that are also common to ItemPlaceholderComparisons.
    EntityComparison
    A kind of ItemComparison that represents the differences between two versions of the same Entity.
    ItemComparison
    A representation of the differences between two versions of the same Item.
    ItemHistory
    Contains the VersionInfos that form the results of a request to retrieve the history of an Item, and an indication of whether the permitted number of results was exceeded.
    ItemMergeInfo
    Information about an Item that has acted as the source in a merge operation, which forms part of a MergeHistory.
    ItemPlaceholderComparison
    A representation of the differences between two versions of the same Item when one or both are only visible as ItemPlaceholders.
    LinkComparison
    A kind of ItemComparison that represents the differences between two versions of the same Link.
    MergeHistory
    Contains the ItemMergeInfos that form the results of a request to retrieve the history of merges into a particular Item.
    MergePopulation
    Contains the ItemIdentifiers of: All the Items that have ever been sources or targets in the chain of merge operations that involves a particular Item The only Item among these that has not been supplanted (and which is therefore the merge product) The Item for which the above information was requested
    MergeProductResult
    The ItemIdentifier of a merge product, and the ItemIdentifier of an Item that has been the source in a merge operation, that together make up a single result of a call to IItemHistoryService.retrieveMergeProducts(java.util.List).
    SourceInfoComparison
    A representation of the differences between two versions of the SourceInfo on the same Card.
    TimestampBoundary
    A Boundary that uses a timestamp to specify one end of a range of Item versions.
    VersionBoundary
    A Boundary that uses a particular version number to specify one end of a range of Item versions.
    VersionInfo
    Information about a version of an Item that forms part of an ItemHistory.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OverflowPolicy
    Indicates how an ItemHistory is populated when the requested range contains more than the maximum number of versions.
